# Context Pack Document References (Pointer)

The authoritative Cursor rules file is at the repository root:

- [/.cursorrules](../.cursorrules)

The mandatory `/docs` context pack referenced by it:

- [architecture.md](architecture.md) — System architecture and design patterns
- [structure.md](structure.md) — Project organization and folder structure
- [code.md](code.md) — Code patterns and conventions
- [dataflow.md](dataflow.md) — Data flow and system boundaries
- [decisions.md](decisions.md) — Architectural decisions and rationale
- [glossary.md](glossary.md) — Domain terminology and definitions
- [risk.md](risk.md) — Security and risk management
